ROBIN ELSON MURDER ACQUITTAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The court is to be commended for its wisdom. Robin Elson is to be praised for 
the courage she finally found to end the life of Jack Elson. 
</P>
