CALIFORNIA STATE UNIVERSITY BOARD OF TRUSTEES; LANSDALE, MARIANTHI; HART, GARY 
K (STATE SEN); DEUKMEJIAN, GEORGE; POLITICAL CONTRIBUTIONS; CALIFORNIA 
GOVERNOR; ETHICS 
</P>
