<P>
Photo, COLOR, An extended stepfamily plays together, from left: Peter and Ceci 
Van Zitter, Brandy and Kelly Van Zitter, and Louise and Roy Van Broekhuizen. 
AURELIO JOSE BARRERA / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
