<P>
REPORTERS; NEWSCASTERS; SPORTSCASTERS; TELEVISION NEWS; HIRING; KTTV 
(TELEVISION STATION); KABC (TELEVISION STATION); LOS ANGELES HERALD EXAMINER 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
