<P>
Full Run 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
SOLIMON, ANWAR S; ARMSTRONG, WAYNE W; DEL TACO NAUGLES INC; FAST FOOD INDUSTRY 
-- UNITED STATES; RESTAURANTS; ACQUISITIONS; LEVERAGED BUYOUTS; MEXICAN FOOD; 
ETHNIC FOODS 
</P>
