solemnly responded to questions the judge asked. Chris Strobel, standing in for 
Robb's court-appointed attorney, Gary Proctor, asked Jameson for a third 
court-appointed psychiatrist to help in Robb's defense, and the judge agreed to 
the request. 
</P>
<P>
Robb has been in detention at Orange County Juvenile Hall since his arrest Oct. 
5, the day the youth is accused of holding classmates at Loara High hostage 
with a handgun and shotgun and shooting Anthony Lopez, 15, in the left side of 
the face. 
